Author: Vishal Raj <vraj0703@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Apr 3 21:23:25 2026 +0530

    fix: sequence camera turn before keyboard appears, fix back-scroll
    
    Camera transition:
    - Delay keyboard visibility from 80% to 93% scroll — camera turn
      (88-93%) now completes fully before keyboard appears, eliminating
      the stall during the turn animation.
    
    Back-scroll from keyboard:
    - Changed hysteresis exit threshold from p<0.93 to p<0.96 — more
      responsive, exits with fewer scroll events.
    - Replaced scrollTo({behavior:'smooth'}) with direct scrollTop
      assignment — smooth scroll fought with drei's internal scroll
      tracking, causing the scroll to feel stuck.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>

